The Village at Ten Trails is a community within a community.

Live amid the stunning natural beauty of the Pacific Northwest, with wooded trails, parks, a town center with retail village, a school and residences all combining to create an interactive atmosphere.
We like to call it your new hometown.
Apartment homes ranging from one to three bedrooms are now pre-leasing, offering high-end finishes, thoughtful touches and comfortable spaces to make your own.
- Private balconies on floors 2 and above
- Centrally located between Maple Valley, Covington, Kent and Enumclaw
